-- =============================================================================
-- SERVICE PAYMENT TERMINAL
-- ServicePaymentTerminal
--
-- Current service module: Hospitality / Dining Hall meals.
--
-- Flow:
--   1. Watch citizen inventory first, then configured/attached dining stock inventories.
--   2. Ignore coal/charcoal only; everything else in dining stock is treated as chargeable stock.
--   3. When food stock decreases, wait the configured eating delay.
--   4. Find the citizen who last increased saturation after that stock decrease.
--   5. Charge that citizen based on food tier * quantity.
--   6. Pay the mapped hospitality company.
--
-- No flat fee.
-- No treasury subsidy.
-- No fake colonist-to-colonist market.
-- =============================================================================

